<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>I agree that the cleric's job is to keep the group alive. However, when I'm in a group that doesn't require large amounts of healing and my mana does not drop below 75% I am going to cast my trusty summoned hammer, load my melee spell set and go up and smack the mobs around a bit (especially if they are undead). I will never do this if we are in a spot that requires my undivided attention on healing. As I said before, main job is healing.</p>
